_json.gridTitle: a comparison of whites | Miss Mustard Seeds Milk Paint
_json.description: I remember a time when white walls and white painted furniture was boring, ho-hum and the default choice of anyone who was afraid of making a decision about color. Now, it’s hot.  It’s the thing.  We all love white and we will use it everywhere! I am definitely digging whites, too, and have been playing with the whites in our line a lot.  I thought I would share how they are each different and distinct, to help you in selecting the white that is right for you! LINEN Linen is our warmest white...
